metadata.name: BORED PEPE #01
metadata.description:
BORED PEPE is a frog community built on the Ethereum blockchain. Their purpose is not to damage the network.

They struggle to exist freely in the NFT world. In total, 99 Pepes will enter the Ethereum blockchain network at regular intervals.

Each PEPE is produced as 1/1 NFT.

by @nrlnft
